title: Flofreedia Pill Ad
description: Written and produced by Crystal Delahanty for Stone Cold Fox's Maude Night show at the UCB Theatre in NYC, 9 March 2009. Shot and edited by John Kingman. Starring D'Arcy Erokan, Fran Gillespie, and Joe Spellman. Voiceover by Crystal Delahanty. Animation by Tao Langston. Thanks to Neil W. Casey.
